## Third-party content

- **Inter** typeface (`fonts/Inter-Variable.ttf`): SIL Open Font License 1.1.
  Copyright Rasmus Andersson and the Inter Project Authors.
  https://github.com/rsms/inter

- **Underlying data sources** (ILOSTAT, GGDC 10-Sector Database, World Bank
  WDI, Bairoch 1988, Mitchell 2003, Cambridge Group, Maddison Project,
  ILO Employment and Social Trends 2026): each carries its own license
  and citation requirements. The Large Labor Model dataset is a derivative
  work that aggregates and reinterprets these sources; users redistributing
  the dataset should consult `methodology-full.html` for the full source list
  and respect the original publishers' terms.

- **AI benchmark sources** (SWE-bench, GPQA, METR, IFR robot density data):
  cited per their published terms in the methodology document.
